to my wife and my superiors.

21:26.410 --> 21:28.829
I also learned that I'd been passed over
for a promotion.

21:29.037 --> 21:32.291
And did you have occasion
to visit Lieutenant Rodriguez that day?

21:32.666 --> 21:34.710
Twice, the first time
to announce the findings

21:34.835 --> 21:36.586
of an ongoing investigation
into the squad.

21:36.878 --> 21:39.881
-JAMES: And what were those findings?
-Detectives moonlighting as bouncers

21:39.965 --> 21:43.135
