associating with dealers and the like.

21:43.343 --> 21:46.430
And why did you choose
to announce your findings that day?

21:46.930 --> 21:50.726
When news of my relationship broke,
I knew the lieutenant had tipped off IAB.

21:51.351 --> 21:53.895
I realized he'd do anything
to stop my investigation,

21:53.979 --> 21:57.733
-so I had to move on him fast.
-Objection as to what the witness knew.

21:58.150 --> 21:59.192
Sustained.

21:59.568 --> 22:03.697
How did Lieutenant Rodriguez
respond to news of your findings?

22:04.072 --> 22:06.074
He was confrontational.

22:06.700 --> 22:09.953
I asked point-blank if he had gone to IAB
about my relationship.

22:10.287 --> 22:13.415
He said that he had, and that one way
or the other, he was gonna be rid of me.

22:13.665 --> 22:14.708
What happened next?

22:14.833 --> 22:17.336
He stood up, said it was me
and him alone in that office,

22:17.586 --> 22:20.339
and with the kind of day I was having,
no one would ask what happened.

22:20.839 --> 22:22.132
Did you ask him what he meant by that?

22:22.215 --> 22:24.134
I didn't need to,
because he went for his gun.

22:24.217 --> 22:26.720
-What did you do?
-I drew my gun and fired.

22:27.095 --> 22:30.891
Did you believe Lieutenant Rodriguez
intended to kill you?

22:31.266 --> 22:32.309
I had no doubt.

22:32.601 --> 22:35.854
And did you then move towards him
with the intention of firing again?

22:36.104 --> 22:39.858
No. I followed proper procedure
by covering him with my gun

22:40.025 --> 22:41.735
with the intent of disarming him.

22:42.569 --> 22:44.404
Next thing I know, I'm shot in the back.

22:45.030 --> 22:47.824
-Are you on suspension now?
-I am.

22:47.991 --> 22:50.035
Is it your intent to return to work?

22:51.328 --> 22:54.956
Regardless of what happens here,
my physical disability will prevent that.

22:55.791 --> 22:58.210
My whole life, all I ever wanted
was to be a cop.

22:59.044 --> 23:03.507
And every day for 18 years,
I was the best cop that I could be.

23:04.216 --> 23:08.136
